uk.ac.cam.darknet.frontend

Class DataProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.darknet.frontend.DataProvider

  • public class DataProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    This class queries the database via a database manager to find the most suitable individuals for an effect. All the data requested is added to the respective individual's Properties object. This class contains overloaded methods suitable for working either with one individual at a time, or with a list of individuals.
    Author:
    Augustin Zidek
